     Welcome to the Fernald Web site. Here’s what’s happening at
     Fernald:

     * The Fernald Site Technology Coordination Group Meeting Minutes for
       Dec. 19, 2001 are now available.

     * Fernald workers have razed  Plant 6.

     * 2002 Greater Cincinnati Regional Science Bowl to be held Feb. 2.

     * Pardon our dust! We just added a new Future section (under "About
       Fernald") to our web and rearranged a few old favorites. Check it
       out!
     * Effective March 1, 2002, the North Access Road will be permanently
       closed to all through traffic. Construction deliveries to the OSDF
       will continue and a connecting gravel road will be provided for
       emergency response vehicles only. For more information contact Bob
       Nichols, 513-648-5180, email: robert.nichols@fernald.gov.


